    "The second is the integration with Security Orchestration Automation and Response (SOAR) which will complement the capabilities of current SIEMs to create a proactive platform for early detection and response to various threats.",
    "The third research direction is to integrate Artificial Intelligence (AI) technologies in the core engines of open-source SIEMs in order to add predictive capabilities for user behavior analytics.",
